title: ‘Classy’: Protesters moon Trump towers in Chicago
text:
‘Classy’: Protesters moon Trump towers in Chicago Posted at 7:24   William A. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
This is the state of anti-Trump protests Sunday: Hundreds are expected to protest by dropping their pants in 30 minutes in front of Trump Tower Chicago. 
— Dan Lopez (@4danlopez) February 12, 2017 A crowd is forming to moon the tower in 15 minutes. I love a public spectacle. #rumpsagainstTrump pic.twitter.com/IXqhh0BNL5 
— Michelle K Stenzel (@MichelleStenzel) February 12, 2017 The mass protest and the object of the mooning. #rumpsagainstTrump #theresistance pic.twitter.com/X2KdCsaYq9 
— Michelle K Stenzel (@MichelleStenzel) February 12, 2017 Hundreds moon the Trump Tower on Chicago's Riverfront https://t.co/qSjWLFDWYt pic.twitter.com/n1Gc5LMTHl 
— FOX 32 News (@fox32news) February 12, 2017 Trending
